    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>/authors/admin/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/authors/admin/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am a graduate student at the &lt;em&gt;Department of Astronomy and Steward Observatory&lt;/em&gt;
at The University of Arizona in Tucson (AZ). I work with Vasilis Paschalidis on
various topics in gravitational physics. In particular, I use and extend the
&lt;a href=&#34;https://einsteintoolkit.org/&#34;&gt;Einstein Toolkit&lt;/a&gt; to perform dynamical-spacetime
simulations of rotating relativistic stars, and of systems with charged black
holes. Moreover, I live inside &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/&#34;&gt;GNU Emacs&lt;/a&gt;,
and my &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arthur_Eddington#Eddington_number_for_cycling&#34;&gt;Eddington
number&lt;/a&gt;
is 22 (but &lt;a href=&#34;img/bike.jpg&#34;&gt;I am working on it&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to know more about me, you can read my &lt;a href=&#34;/doc/cv_bozzola.pdf&#34;&gt;academic curriculum
vitae&lt;/a&gt; or you can &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:gabrielebozzola@arizona.edu&#34;&gt;send me an
email&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
